node.text:
Finally! I am happy to present you my 2025 Calendar! 😊

This year, I’ve created two versions: one features my favorite photographs of European wildlife and the second one is from my recent adventure in the Amazon Rainforest.

Each photo reminds me of a different story. From enduring frozen fingers while waiting 8h hidden in the sunflower field for goldfinches to appear; crawling in the 40cm of deep snow to capture the perfect angle of a group of Whooper Swans; to climbing trees in the Peruvian rainforest and photographing the most colorful birds I’ve ever seen.

Calendars are available in English and Polish. Each image is captioned with the species name and the location. On the last page you’ll also find a link to behind-the-scenes stories and fun facts!

The number of calendars is limited. 

You can order the calendars now through the link in my bio 😊 Shipping worldwide 🌎

⬆️ LINK IN BIO ⬆️

P.S. I can also DM you the link to the calendar if you comment “parrot” 🦜
